{"tid":1967220,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人已經唔想再拍拖結婚?","createTime":"2020-04-10T18:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T18:20:08.000Z","uid":128120,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d785317fae36f569f593ea03a8571322fb00dee4","tid":1967220,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"講真屌閪可以叫雞<br />\n或者上一上tinder求其都食到幾件<br />\n又唔洗負責任,錢又睇你叫開咩質素而定<br />\n拍拖結婚又限制住你做好多野<br />\n可能你話點都會寂寞 想有人陪<br />\n但當你習慣左一個人 其實好撚爽<br />\n當你做廢青 每個人搵得萬幾<br />\nd錢洗係自己身上不之幾好洗<br />\n又唔洗煩結婚d開支<br />\n拍拖洗費又唔洗用<br />\n久而久之做到好多自己想做既野<br />\n人生就係做自己想做既野架麻<br />\n唔通好似一條公式? 拍拖&gt;結婚&gt;生仔&gt;等死?<br />\n我已經諗通左<br />\n既然咁樣做可以日日開心過下日神<br />\n做咩要咁辛苦?<br />\n不如搵綜援再每個月番十日左右parttime已經有尼個生活<br />\n幾撚爽"},{"pid":"324f31a1a4342a01308897ab2cab5c47a3ecff83","tid":1967220,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073d8be92c1d14e5aa3210f5f2b63932a5cf6e52","tid":1967220,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁辛苦幫人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8102a017b320b6b564c85c8cdd4f7a09bc2f8d76","tid":1967220,"uid":134863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"324f31a1a4342a01308897ab2cab5c47a3ecff83","tid":1967220,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"你唔記得轉account"},{"pid":"d432ca6ee60c3aaa5080032b6b9670acef003bc1","tid":1967220,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8102a017b320b6b564c85c8cdd4f7a09bc2f8d76","tid":1967220,"uid":134863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"324f31a1a4342a01308897ab2cab5c